dct_title_s: Inland Waterway from Cape May to Bay Head - Sheet 1 I
dct_description_sm: Map covers Cape May County from Cape May Point Borough to Ocean City. Map shows the waterways. It shows the section of the route that needs to be dredged for the 8 foot channel and the section of the route that needs no dredging, along with the profile of the cubic yards to be dredged for the 8 foot channel and the 10 foot channel.
